    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>There is an urgent need to ameliorate the transport of the reconstituted vaccines to the vaccination sites to improve the COVID-19 vaccination campaigns. The maintenance of the integrity of the mRNA of the different COVID-19 reconstituted vaccines after continuous movement at room temperature during at least three hours ensures the safety of a ground transportation.</jats:p>",
